{"type": "article", "id": 18493, "title": "面包机", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-04T07:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152234UJdyQETO47P1lw6p.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个面包机，设计师 James Stumpf 用竹子和玻璃做结构，想让面包机变得透明。你可以看侧面的电子时钟，也可以直接透过玻璃查看面包是否熟了。因为玻璃的通透感，它的体积显得更小，而在玻璃上用红线勾出几圈框架，让它看上去有设计感。<a href=\"http://stumpfstudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152232PWeZQh5X84BYd6Dt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.77148438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152233ptkFSzd2m6ODnIrE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76367188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152233DzLFyAcRZY34MxXG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.88574219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}